OL,3,CPensioner who killed eight-year-old
OL,4,Cgirl to be given suspended sentence
OL,6,FA Co Antrim pensioner who knocked down
OL,7,Fand killed an eight-year old
OL,8,Fschoolgirl will be handed a suspended
OL,9,Fsentence, a court heard on Monday.
OL,11,FScarlett Rossborough died after being
OL,12,Fstruck by a car driven by John Noble
OL,13,FLindsay on High Street in
OL,14,FCarrickfergus in August 2023.
OL,16,FLindsay, who is 92 and from Prince
OL,17,FAndrew Way in Carrick, admitted a
OL,18,Fcharge of causing Scarlett's death by
OL,19,Fdangerous driving.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/15
