OL,3,CPensioner who killed eight-year-old
OL,4,Cgirl to be given suspended sentence
OL,6,FHe is currently in hospital and was
OL,7,Fexcused from attending today's hearing
OL,8,Fat Belfast Crown Court.
OL,10,FGiving her judgement in the case,
OL,11,FJudge Patricia Smyth said she will be
OL,12,Fimposing a ten-month sentence upon
OL,13,FLindsay, which will be suspended for
OL,14,F12 months, "when he is well enough" to
OL,15,Fbe sentenced.
OL,17,FThe former RUC officer will also be
OL,18,Fbanned from driving for five years by
OL,19,FJudge Patricia Smyth.
