OL,4,Cgirl to be given suspended sentence
OL,6,FThe Belfast Recorder said: "The
OL,7,Fenormity of the tragedy cannot be put
OL,8,Finto words.
OL,10,F"Scarlett was a beautiful, happy
OL,11,Fchild, loved by all who knew her. She
OL,12,Fwas eight years old and described as
OL,13,Fthe princess of the family.
OL,15,F"She was the kindest, most sensitive,
OL,16,Fempathetic little person. She was
OL,17,Fdetermined and passionate."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/15
