OL,3,CPensioner who killed eight-year-old
OL,4,Cgirl to be given suspended sentence
OL,6,FRevealing that Scarlett loved sports,
OL,7,Fmusic and was a keen artist and
OL,8,Fgymnast who loved to play with her
OL,9,Flittle brother, Judge Smyth said:
OL,10,F"There is no sentence that I can pass
OL,11,Fthat will bring any comfort to
OL,12,FScarlett's parents and family, who
OL,13,Fhave suffered so much.
OL,15,F"The shocking circumstances of her
OL,16,Fdeath have affected so many people and
OL,17,Fnothing can turn back the clock and
OL,18,Frestore the precious young life that
OL,19,Fhas been lost."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/15
