OL,3,CPensioner who killed eight-year-old
OL,4,Cgirl to be given suspended sentence
OL,6,FOn the day in question Scarlett - who
OL,7,Fattended Linn Primary School in Larne
OL,8,F- was amongst a group of children and
OL,9,Fadult leaders from a local community
OL,10,Fcentre summer scheme enjoying a day
OL,11,Fout to Carrick Castle.
OL,13,FCrown barrister David Russell KC said
OL,14,Fthat as the group was walking along
OL,15,Fthe footpath on High Street, Lindsay's
OL,16,Fcar mounted the footpath and struck
OL,17,Fthree children.
OL,19,FPrior to the collision, Lindsay had
OL,20,Fparked his car in a disabled parking
OL,21,Fspace.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/15
