OL,3,CPensioner who killed eight-year-old
OL,4,Cgirl to be given suspended sentence
OL,6,FMr Russell said that after initially
OL,7,Fparking his car, Lindsay was captured
OL,8,Fon CCTV exiting the vehicle then
OL,9,Fgetting back into the car.
OL,11,FHe then attempted to re-park the car
OL,12,Fand began moving the vehicle backwards
OL,13,Fand forwards several times.
OL,15,FSaying this was "presumably an effort
OL,16,Fto move his car closer to the kerb",
OL,17,FMr Russell said "as the car reversed
OL,18,Fonce more, with the front wheel
OL,19,Fsteered to the right, it's movement
OL,20,Fwas initially slow before suddenly
OL,21,Faccelerating.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/15
