OL,6,F"The car mounted the footpath,
OL,7,Fstriking Scarlett and at least two
OL,8,Fother children, then collided with the
OL,9,Fwall of an adjacent building, trapping
OL,10,FScarlett between the rear of the
OL,11,Fvehicle and the wall."
OL,13,FTwo other children were thrown into
OL,14,Fthe doorway of a shop but didn't
OL,15,Fsuffer any serious injury.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/15
