OL,6,FIn the direct aftermath of the
OL,7,Fcollision, members of the public
OL,8,Frushed to help and signalled for
OL,9,FLindsay to move his car forward, and
OL,10,Fboth the PSNI and Ambulance Service
OL,11,Fattended the scene.
OL,13,FDue to the catastrophic injuries that
OL,14,Fshe sustained, Scarlett could not be
OL,15,Fsaved.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/15
