OL,6,FMr Russell said that at the point of
OL,7,Fimpact, Lindsay's car was travelling
OL,8,Fbetween 11 and 12 mph and that "pedal
OL,9,Fmisapplication" could have been a
OL,10,Fpossible cause of the collision, as
OL,11,Fcould confusion on Lindsay's part.
OL,13,FHe added there was no suggestion or
OL,14,Fevidence to indicate that Lindsay
OL,15,Fdeliberately steered his vehicle onto
OL,16,Fthe footpath.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/15
