OL,6,FPolice spoke to Lindsay at the scene
OL,7,Fand when he was asked what happened,
OL,8,Fhe replied 'I don't know' and said he
OL,9,Fhad been trying to get into the
OL,10,Fparking space.
OL,12,FHe was interviewed on August 29 and in
OL,13,Fa pre-prepared statement, he accepted
OL,14,Fbeing the driver and that his vehicle
OL,15,Fmounted the footpath.
OL,17,FLindsay also accepted hitting a wall
OL,18,Fand, in the statement, he said he was
OL,19,Fnot initially aware of a collision
OL,20,Fwith a pedestrian.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/15
