OL,6,FMr Russell said Lindsay "ultimately
OL,7,Faccepted he collided with Scarlett and
OL,8,Fthe other children" and "expressed his
OL,9,Fcondolences both to Scarlett's family
OL,10,Fand the other children involved."
OL,12,FDefence barrister Frank O'Donoghue KC
OL,13,Fsaid: "The defendant has always
OL,14,Faccepted full responsibility for what
OL,15,Foccurred. His guilt is total and his
OL,16,Ffeelings of guilt are unrelenting
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/15
