OL,3,CPensioner who killed eight-year-old
OL,4,Cgirl to be given suspended sentence
OL,6,F"The defendant has been devastated by
OL,7,Fwhat has occurred and he is fully
OL,8,Faware of the unrelenting suffering
OL,9,Fthat he has brought, by his actions,
OL,10,Fto Scarlett's parents, siblings, step-
OL,11,Fmother, grandparents and wider family
OL,12,Fcircle."
OL,14,FThe barrister said his client was "a
OL,15,Fman who, up to this point, lived an
OL,16,Fexemplary life" and that "in over 70
OL,17,Fyear of driving he never so much as
OL,18,Freceived a parking tickets, let alone
OL,19,Fa penalty point, let alone being
OL,20,Fconvicted of any driving offence."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/15
