OL,3,CPensioner who killed eight-year-old
OL,4,Cgirl to be given suspended sentence
OL,6,FMr O'Donoghue revealed that the day
OL,7,Fafter "this dreadful accident", his
OL,8,Fclient "surrendered his licence and he
OL,9,Fnever drove again."
OL,11,FHe also spoke of Lindsay's
OL,12,Fdeteriorating health, with the court
OL,13,Fhearing that a recent medical report
OL,14,Fdetermined his life expectancy to be
OL,15,Fbetween nine months to a year.
OL,17,FDuring today's hearing, Judge Smyth
OL,18,Fspoke of the loss suffered by
OL,19,FScarlett's family, many of whom set
OL,20,Fout their grief in Victim Impact
OL,21,FStatements.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/15
