OL,6,FThis included Scarlett's mother who
OL,7,Fhas been left 'haunted' by the tragedy
OL,8,Fand who has called for a new law -
OL,9,FScarlett's Law - which would ban very
OL,10,Felderly people from driving in the
OL,11,Finterests of the public.
OL,13,FJudge Smyth also noted that Scarlett's
OL,14,Ffather's life has been "ripped apart"
OL,15,Fby what happened to his daughter.
OL,17,FSaying this case "highlights the very
OL,18,Freal risk that elderly drivers pose to
OL,19,Fother road users", Judge Smyth said:
OL,20,F"If anything good can come out of
OL,21,Fthis, it will be a new Scarlett's Law."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/15
