OL,6,FIn Lindsay's absence, the Judge spoke
OL,7,Fof "exceptional circumstances" in the
OL,8,Fcase including his "extreme age", his
OL,9,Fill health, the limited life
OL,10,Fexpectancy and his previous
OL,11,F"unblemished character" - and ruled
OL,12,Fthat an immediate prison sentence will
OL,13,Fnot be imposed.
